rComments: Going to class isn't going to get you a good grade if you don't do the readings! They're so important for this course. If you take it seriously you'll find the course and his grading to be very fair! He's also very nice and approachable so ask questions if you need to and he'll try his best to help.
He is helpful, but his classes were on the boring side. The tutorials were fun. His exams were challenging.
He's probably one of the most nicest proffs. He really tries to help out his students. He's the cutest proff!!!
